Nobody governs the context input layer. Tools exist to govern what agents DO (Microsoft AGT), what agents SAY (Guardrails AI), and how agents COMMUNICATE (NeMo). But the data flowing INTO the context window — retriever results, tool outputs, agent messages — is completely ungoverned. That's what Provena fixes&lt;/p&gt;
